OL,5,G2300 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,6,     FWith Franky's hold growing in the
OL,7,     Fprison, temperatures reach boiling
OL,8,     Fpoint in an all-out riot in which
OL,9,     FBill gets stabbed.
OL,10,G0005 Prisoner: Cell Block H
